sonderer Berücksichtigung der Unterschiede zu den AUB 99, 94, 88 und 61. Damit liefert der Band die umfassendste Kommentierung der Unfallversicherung nach der VVG-Reform und neuer AUB.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aInsurance law. 0aInsurance policies. 4aVersicherungsvertrag / Kommentar. 7aLAW / Corporate.2bisacsh1 aLeverenz, Kent, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Law - 2000 - 2014z9783110636208oZDB-23-GLA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2011z9783110261189oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET RECHTSWISSENSCHAFTEN 2011z9783110261264oZDB-23-DGC0 cprintz978389949509640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311024861640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110248616423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110248616/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGCb2011  aZDB-23-DGGb2011  aZDB-23-GLAc2000d2014